## ğŸŒ± About E.M.O.R.A

**E.M.O.R.A** is an anonymous mental health support platform designed to help people navigate loneliness, emotional distress, and mental well-being without fear of judgment.

Inspired by the film ***Her*** and aligned with **UN Sustainable Development Goal 3: Good Health & Well-Being**, E.M.O.R.A blends **professional care**, **AI guidance**, and **community support** into one calm, human-centered experience.

Whether someone needs immediate grounding, long-term support, or simply a space to express themselves â€” E.M.O.R.A is there.

